data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!  This hard to find home is a haven in so many ways! It boasts  both a living room and a family room, each with their own fireplace, one is wood burning and the other is gas. The lovely master bedroom has a full master bath, and 2 closets, one being a walk-in. There is a ¾ bath near the other 3 bedrooms and the dining room. There is an additional ¼  bath attached to a large bedroom as well.You will find this spacious home located on a dead end road and nestled in a serene, natural setting of trees, bushes, and a manicured lawn. The short sturdy bridge in the driveway crosses the seasonal irrigation ditch. Having a channel of running water not only adds to the charm, but is functional in watering the lawn in the summer months. There are several places to park including the garage, which has an automatic opener. Additionally, there is an extra large, detached shop which has two sides, one with a roll up door. There is also a shed and a lean-to in the backyard. The optional hot tub is an experience in both winter and summer. The wildlife that frequent this lot add to our treasured Montana lifestyle. This home is worth checking out!
